These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, salsa, reggae, rock
1. the fan of funk is on the left of the fan of rock##1
2. the fan of salsa is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
3. the fan of funk is on the right of the fan of salsa##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | salsa | funk | rock |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-2::.
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, frog, dog, pony
1. the owner of the pony is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| Pet   | hedgehog | dog | frog | pony |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, hiking, camping, cooking
1. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby   | camping | collecting | hiking | cooking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-4::.
