1. the person driving the ship is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |  2   |    3    |  4  |
| Transport   | ship | skateboard | tram | motorbike |

